&lt;p&gt;The activity uses Google Jamboard and was developed for my computer logic and organization class on the topic of function prologues/epilogues in ARM assembly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mark Gondree, &lt;a href="https://ocs.calstate.edu/quarry/exemplar/162"&gt;"Small Group Activity using Jamboard"&lt;/a&gt;, developed 6/22/2021, accepted into QuARRy 1/5/2022.&lt;/p&gt;
